      "content": "### SEO & Search Engine Optimization\n- **Dynamic meta tags for shareable content**: Story/article pages need dynamic OpenGraph (og:title, og:description, og:image, og:url) and Twitter Card meta tags generated from database content; JSON-LD Article schema with structured data (headline, description, image, datePublished, author) enables Google rich snippets; XSS-safe content escaping prevents injection attacks; separate `/robots.txt` and `/sitemap.xml` routes guide crawlers to published content; sitemap.xml dynamically lists all published items enabling discovery; static HTML pages (homepage, browse, reader) need comprehensive meta tags with canonical URLs; favicon on",
