      "content": "### Dashboard & Analytics\n- **Dashboard MVP pattern**: Responsive Tailwind design with summary cards, CRUD forms, real-time updates; pair database schema (PostgreSQL tables with standard fields: id, user_id, created_at, updated_at) with clean API endpoints; interactive data grid with inline edit/delete and form validation; landing page with direct link to dashboard feature; enables rapid portfolio management UI deployment\n- **Calendar/scheduling UI pattern**: Interactive calendar component (day/week/month views) with fast navigation; bookings/events created inline or via modal; real-time state updates without full page reload; indexed database queries (date ranges, user filtering) ensure sub-second response times; combine with revenue/analytics summary sidebar for operational dashboard\n- **Analytics dashboard pattern**: Summary cards (metrics at a glance), interactive charts (bar charts for distributions, dual-axis line charts for trends), data tables (top items, performance metrics), date controls (7/30 day toggle, refresh button) provide unified visibility into application performance; usage metrics dashboard shows quota consumption, billing period status, cost breakdown by service",
