      "content": "## Database & Connection Pooling\n- **Pool**: 25 connections, `connectionTimeoutMillis: 10s`, `idleTimeoutMillis: 30s`\n- **Key tables**: `job_applications` (`applied_at` NOT `created_at`), `work_experience` (NOT NULL: `company_name`, `title`), `candidate_skills` (`level` INT 1-5), `portfolio_projects` (`title` NOT NULL), `offers` (30 cols, `title` NOT NULL), `practice_sessions`, `feedback`, `question_bank` (category/difficulty tags), `mock_sessions`, `tts_cache`, `activity_log`, `country_configs` (8 seeded), `payroll_*` (5 tables), `scheduled_interviews`, `interviews` (`interview_type` NOT `type`), `jobs`, `pipeline_stages` (7 canonical: Applied, Screening, Phone Screen, Technical, Offer, Accepted, Rejected), `memory_events`, `memory_objects`, `memory_relationships`, `recruiter_preferences`, `candidate_match_breakdown` (7D), `match_feedback`, `communications`, `communication_templates`, `communication_sequences`, `communication_enrollments`, `ai_call_log`, `ai_prompts`, `ai_prompt_versions`, `ai_ab_tests`\n- **Phase 5 tables** (Feb 2026): `screening_templates`, `screening_invites`, `screening_responses`, `interview_evaluators`, `interview_evaluations`, `scheduled_interview_reminders`, `assessments`, `assessment_questions`, `assessment_responses`\n- **Dashboard persistence tables**: `ai_provider_verification`, `ai_token_usage`, `ai_provider_stats`, `ai_model_metrics`\n- **Query optimization**: DISTINCT + ORDER BY requires all ORDER BY columns in SELECT; slow queries >200ms tracked",
